sentences.english: Clean and bright, You look happy to meet me.

sentences.english: I hadn't seen Gordy in years, but the boy always liked to showboat .

sentences.english: and you have a lot of Africans in London.

sentences.english: Min hao knocked over the dishes, told Xia Chan dint want to see her again.

sentences.english: Good morning, boys and girls. Nice to see you. I am Mrs Zhou .
sentences.chinese: 同学们早上好，我是周老师，见到你们很高兴。

sentences.english: Only my work helped me forget what I was seeing. "——H. S."

sentences.english: I think many people are willing to see, the Poyang Lake, is also not because other.

预见到会有亏损，雍容大度地接受亏损。

sentences.english: Is it possible fme to see the harbour in person today?

sentences.english: Mrs. Taylor and Mr. Zhou meet on the street.

sentences.english: I'm dying to see my sweetheart.
Both my parents are dead and I rarely see my two sisters.
sentences.chinese: 我的爸妈都死了，我很少见到我的两个妹妹。

sentences.english: All the way in the train the rails kept singing, "You're going to see Daddy-Long-Legs."
sentences.chinese: 一路上，铁轨都在唱着“你就要见到长腿叔叔了。”

sentences.english: I hope I can meet you at Jack's home on Sunday. Allright?
